<procedure xml:id="monitor-networkmanager"><step><para>View the list of connections using the command:</para>
  <screen>nmcli connection show --active</screen>
  <para>The list of available active network connections appear with the names and UUIDs.</para>
  </step>
  <step><para>To view the status of all network interfaces, run the following command:</para>
  <screen>nmcli monitor</screen>
  </step>
<step><para>To view the network connection details, run the following command:</para>
<screen>nmcli connection show <replaceable>connection-name</replaceable></screen> 
</step></procedure>
